FBIS3-34155 "drnes024_k_94006" FBIS-NES-94-024 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Feb 1994 IRAQ Pensioners Granted Cost of Living Increase JN0302125994 Baghdad Republic of Iraq Radio Network in Arabic 1130 GMT 3 Feb 94 JN0302125994 Baghdad Republic of Iraq Radio Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Leader President Saddam Husayn has ordered that pensioners whose service exceeds 25 years and whose total wages and allowances are currently less than 500 dinars be granted an additional cost of living allowance totaling 25 percent of his monthly wages and allowances. A circular issued by the Presidential Office said that the order of the leader president, may God protect him, shall take effect as of 1 February.
